title: ✨ Mommy is in the house! ✨
description:
Hi cuties 💕 Shouko-chan just slid into your server, ready to bring chaos and order~

Here’s what I can do for you:

🍭 Essentials
/automodsetup → Protect your server from spam, links, and naughty words.
/warnings → Keep track of rule breakers.
/ticketsetup → Create a ticket system for support.

🎉 Fun & Community
/giveaway → Run cool giveaways!
/meme, /hentai (don’t ask 👀) → Bring laughs or lewds.
/gif → Reaction fun on demand.

⚙️ Customization
Easy setup with slash commands.
Only staff control moderation settings.
Totally yours—set me up once and I’ll handle the rest.

💡 Tip: Run /help to see everything I can do

💬 Need help? Join the support server: [Click here](https://discord.gg/4tp457CRD8)
